{"tid":1789073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推上國際！禮義廉梁志祥用納粹主義比喻香港示威者！","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T08:04:16.000Z","uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e996129d7776e29b8b5a09ccd96ebb9e4d7013","tid":1789073,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"立法會合併辯論3項涉及6.12衝突的議案，要求引用《權力及特權法》調查事件及傳召官員作供。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯梁志祥指出，6月12日是隨後暴力事件的序幕，形容目前情況猶如納粹主義，不少人對暴力行為拍掌歡呼，指香港在黑色恐怖中，將難以發展。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨黃碧雲則批評政府無視和平示威堅持如期修例，才引發市民6月12日包圍立法會，又指當日有警員向她和其他議員施放催淚水劑，9月向警察投訴課投訴至今，仍未有進展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2333561/梁志祥%3A6.12屬暴力序幕+目前情況如納粹主義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2333561%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E7%A5%A5%253A6.12%E5%B1%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%8F%E5%B9%95%2B%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E5%A6%82%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=2f9c5e86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2333561/梁志祥%3A6.12屬暴力序幕+目前情況如納粹主義</a><br />\n<br />\n眾所鳩之，外國人特別係德國人最唔鍾意人隨便搬納粹出黎抽水<br />\n經過上次猶差之後仲未知死<br />\n今次你條鄉黑梁志祥仲唔仆街陷家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1933d540e759554fee03fededf31f4dd98c247","tid":1789073,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGXOOIBxzLj